FBIS3-51267 "drlat011_o_94016" FBIS-LAT-94-011 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Jan 1994 Colombia Gaviria Meets With Minister PA1701150194 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network in Spanish 1432 GMT 17 Jan 94 PA1701150194 Santa Fe de Bogota Emisoras Caracol Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "Up-to-the-Minute" newscast] [Text] Rudolf Hommes, minister of finance and public credit, is now meeting with President Cesar Gaviria to assess the attempt against his life -- in which he was not hurt -- and his security situation. The Presidential Palace and its perimeter are under military control, and special security measures are being implemented throughout the city.
